        "content": "<p>I just happened to notice that <a href=\"http://test.fhir.org\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://test.fhir.org\">test.fhir.org</a> uses the syntax <code>_sort:asc=birthdate / _sort:desc=birthdate</code> to flip between ascending and descending sort order in search Bundles. The spec however says <code>_sort=birthdate / _sort=-birthdate</code>,<br>\nwhich leads to an exeption on this server.<br>\nWhat gives...?</p>",
        "id": 159140011,
        "sender_full_name": "Simone Heckmann",
        "timestamp": 1550824640
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"191316\">@Grahame Grieve</span> ..?</p>",
