        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1550829275
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>No, I checked R4 spec, and it still has STU3 syntax: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/implement/standards/fhir/search.html#sort\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://hl7.org/implement/standards/fhir/search.html#sort\">http://hl7.org/implement/standards/fhir/search.html#sort</a></p>",
        "id": 159147323,
        "sender_full_name": "Simone Heckmann",
        "timestamp": 1550832681
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ah no, it changed from DSTU2 (<a href=\"http://www.hl7.org/fhir/DSTU2/search.html#sort\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://www.hl7.org/fhir/DSTU2/search.html#sort\">http://www.hl7.org/fhir/DSTU2/search.html#sort</a>) to STU3 :D</p>",
